rows.label: tlk4235012501_msg0001
rows.name: Welcome to this remote place, mo.

rows.label: tlk4235012501_msg0002
rows.name:
Are you a traveler, mo? If so, I
have nothing to sell you, mo.

rows.label: tlk4235012501_msg0003
rows.name:
Mokumoku deals in lumber for building
houses and furniture, mo. Lumber
is useless on a journey, mo.

rows.label: tlk4235012501_msg0004
rows.name:
If you want to carry it around
wildly on your shoulder, I won't
tell you not to buy it, but... mo.
